    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_4849fa84488352507b8d1a89",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "这只是一些一般设置，在我们页面上设置了无衬线的字体、使用  模型，去掉  默认外边距。",
        "text_hash": "f861b4ed6b4ad6e00fdaf389e8ca8c1e8691427913ac3af3f0ed2b8584ab04dd",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d0170393c3c9c661f72b0e0c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "下一步，在你早先的 CSS 下面加入如下代码：",
        "text_hash": "5fb1dd4a17a3855dd1e84aebb108a478cfaf6c0a426b9d22005c30a17b86a9e9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8de395386a618524c8eb12b3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "css\n.info-box {\n  width: 450px;\n  height: 400px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}",
        "text_hash": "4db91b5d36d37066001e442985be6e22f3b994090c173d43357322831a5be476",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ab137ae5ca479b7eb8f5ff20",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "这对内容设置具体的高度和宽度、在屏幕居中使用老把戏 margin: 0 auto 。在早先的课程中我们建议尽可能不固定内容容器的高度。这个情况下是可以的，因为我们是在选项卡中固定的内容，如果每个标签都有不同的高度，看起来也有些不和谐。",
        "text_hash": "800c106d39ef5e9f611da4fe92a75543548072ee82ef765ae5fae755928ec910",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_16d2f2b30637c1e56401ab41",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "样式化我们的选项卡",
        "text_hash": "f888b226367e24165cfb93a55df2622ed0fddf8336666fefd6896c8427c378ef",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_68f83dcba2d234e1c4a0208b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "现在我们希望样式化选项卡看上去像选项卡——基本，这些是一个水平的导航标签，但不是点击之后加载不同的网页，和我们之前在课程中见到的不同，相反，他们在同一页面上显示不同的面板。首先，在你的 CSS 底部添加下列规则，从无序列表中移除默认的和值：",
        "text_hash": "ed62de813f3fa45284d9ba4cd8b0542ce9547a01387f2bb64ea89fbdb00a4a46",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_2ca32c4cf443a120571cae76",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "css\n.info-box ul {\n  padding-left: 0;\n  margin-top: 0;\n}",
        "text_hash": "a15b855780b9017010b3a9d8e78da67f72a43e2dc26dc860411811b8b7d762ce",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ed3a1ccb013e3dd3bc5b5d72",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "[!NOTE]\n我们正在使用后代选择器，整个例子 .info-box 都位于链的开始——这样页面已经带有其他内容时，我们可以插入这个特征，不害怕与应用于页面其他部分的样式冲突。",
        "text_hash": "0d9002e9e573cc7ae3c83f4409591f2ec134faa7e096460738b6e7cf56c8cfae",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "quotation"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_eaa3f7f3dd36ed48d0c130cc",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "接下来，我们将样式化水平选项卡——列表项都要左浮动确保他们一行合起来，他们的被设置为 none 用以去除项目符号，宽度（）设置为 150px 以便于适应这个 info-box。链接（  ）元素设置为 inline-block，这样他们将在一行显示，仍然保持样式可设置，他们会被样式化合适的选项卡按钮，通过一系列的其他属性。",
        "text_hash": "0154225ef1dcdc17b565845fb912fbb9406ee5fc9f43c52dd1466efde4ca8b1c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e44f4f9bf805858b0a40f55e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "添加下列的 CSS：",
        "text_hash": "fc8880f06b94675b800591f384d0d216b240a55326588837587d2800ca8482e5",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
