    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b731342e53b16371b4be0885",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "首先，添加下列的规则去样式化 .panels  容器。我们简单的设置一个固定的高度，确保面板包含在 info-box 里面， relative 设置  为定位上下文，这样你能然后相对自身放置定位子元素，而不是相对元素，最后我们清除（）浮动，设置在上面 CSS 中，这样避免影响布局的剩余部分。",
        "text_hash": "607cf75c6dc73d07f7524b202aef531f2196b09d4b3f2b2d2d76ed605ec6aa0f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f30182638725f112daa9ceb5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "css\n.info-box .panels {\n  height: 352px;\n  position: relative;\n  clear: both;\n}",
        "text_hash": "8a93a781afbcfad6057c10dba1ebfccddc59bb5ae53fef83a6a3d2e7e19834e7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
