      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c597b1b4e8e9bc7be9163c48",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "第二条规则是在实际的   元素的 checkbox 上设置 属性为 absolute，并从屏幕上方隐藏掉它，我们并不希望在我们的用户界面里看到它。",
        "text_hash": "3cc45522e6d8e6d383715128d84abdfbfaff1dc7be2281a35e825df6816ced31",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_885d9ba5aac5d4c424b0c97b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "设置面板的样式",
        "text_hash": "105e5fb4019de3bdb2e6dfb0f36a362e2f95a759dd4c67e98163bf487ff50cad",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_93cf86f3255c5a581b607f71",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "现在是时候为实际的滑动面板设计风格了。在你的 css 底部添加下列规则：",
        "text_hash": "fea1e05eec353dca4616c56de0ddbce8e87d65e1be4b9bb3942ab4d48d84b5b0",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_736e80594ffac22976508677"
